cc:Work.dc:title: Inkscape 0.92.3's Bevels
cc:Work.dc:description: A reference of Inkscape 0.92.3's (pre-installed) bevels. Showcase objects are a rectangle, a circle and a spiral with its stroke converted to path. Fonts used are Mr De Haviland, Noto Sans, Roboto Condensed, and Noto Sans Light Condensed.
